'''青藏战争'''是1932年因为[[西藏|西藏]][[噶廈|噶廈]]政府想从中国西北[[马家军|马家军]]手中夺取[[青海|青海]][[玉树藏族自治州|玉树地区]]的控制权而爆发的一场战争。

1932年，受[[英国|英国]]支持的西藏方面想将当时与[[西康|西康]]方面[[刘文辉|刘文辉]]（时西康省主席）的战事扩大化，转而开始向青海进军。3月，[[藏军|藏军]]以玉树地区隶属权有争议的寺庙[[尕丹寺|尕丹寺]]黄白教派冲突为借口，开始进攻<ref>[http://www.qh.xinhuanet.com/2009-11/14/content_18232222_1.htm 青藏战争的内幕] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924083534/http://www.qh.xinhuanet.com/2009-11/14/content_18232222_1.htm |date=2015-09-24 }} 新华网青海频道  2009-11-14  2014-10-22查阅</ref>。青海回民将军[[马步芳|马步芳]]大破藏军，并将西康的[[石渠县|石渠县]]、[[德格县|德格县]]等自1919年即被藏军所占县份收回<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ak3SQTVS7acC&pg=PA150|title=''The historical status of China's Tibet''|author=Jiawei Wang, Nimajianzan|year=1997|publisher=五洲传播出版社|location=|page=150|isbn=7-80113-304-8|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001060650/http://books.google.com/books?id=ak3SQTVS7acC&pg=PA150&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&hl=en&ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=7&ved=0CEUQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=ma%20bufang%20liu%20wenhui&f=false|archive-date=2014-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&ct=result&id=0bsKAAAAYAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang|title=''The biographies of the Dalai Lamas''|author=Hanzhang Ya|year=1991|publisher=Foreign Languages Press|location=|pages=352,355,442| isbn=0-8351-2266-2|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928154019/http://books.google.com/books?ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&ct=result&id=0bsKAAAAYAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang|archive-date=2014-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?ei=qRwhTMCjKIWdlgfoo6HAAQ&ct=result&id=Rh1uAAAAMAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang|title=''India & China, 1904–2004: a century of peace and conflict''|author=B. R. Deepak| year=2005|publisher=Manak Publications| location=|page=82|isbn=81-7827-112-5|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928154023/http://books.google.com/books?ei=qRwhTMCjKIWdlgfoo6HAAQ&ct=result&id=Rh1uAAAAMAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang|archive-date=2014-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>，藏军被迫退至[[金沙江|金沙江]]另一侧<ref>{{cite conference|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MJ-dCe_MppgC&pg=PA66|title=''Khams pa histories: visions of people, place and authority'' |book-title=Proceedings of the 9th Seminar of the International Association for Tibetan Studies, Leiden 2000|author=Peng WenBin| conference=International Association for Tibetan Studies Seminar|editor=Lawrence Epstein| year=2002|publisher=BRILL|location=|page=66|isbn=90-04-12423-3|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140930172542/http://books.google.com/books?id=MJ-dCe_MppgC&pg=PA66&lpg=PA66&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&source=bl&ots=G_fKHfaKkq&sig=O4wJ_esItGQzweTi3_4aodGFDVM&hl=en&ei=thohTN6GM4X7lweX84TgDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CBYQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=ma%20bufang%20liu%20wenhui&f=false|archive-date=2014-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GRRynCRRCkwC&pg=PA172|title=''Tibetan Buddhists in the making of modern China''|author=Gray Tuttle|year=2005|publisher=Columbia University Press| location=|page=172| isbn=0-231-13446-0|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928135039/http://books.google.com/books?id=GRRynCRRCkwC&pg=PA172&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&hl=en&ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CDgQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=ma%20bufang%20liu%20wenhui&f=false|archive-date=2014-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。青海军大捷使得藏军在西康[[甘孜县|甘孜]]和[[新龙|新龙]]两地的补给线收到严重威胁，因而开始撤军。马刘二人警告藏军不要跨过金沙江<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=mpqApZWrJyIC&pg=PA89&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&hl=en&ei=FhshTPnEIYS8lQfz4rinAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDMQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=ma%20bufang%20liu%20wenhui&f=false|title=''Frontier passages: ethnopolitics and the rise of Chinese communism, 1921–1945''|author=Xiaoyuan Liu|year=2004|publisher=Stanford University Press|location=|page=89|isbn=0-8047-4960-4|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034257/http://books.google.com/books?id=mpqApZWrJyIC&pg=PA89&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&hl=en&ei=FhshTPnEIYS8lQfz4rinAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDMQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=ma%20bufang%20liu%20wenhui&f=false|archive-date=2014-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月2日夜，青海军援军与守军配合，彻底击溃包围[[结古|结古]]的藏军，藏军损失惨重<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.yushunews.com/system/2010/07/21/010163652.shtml |title=玉树州新闻网-历史沿革 |access-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022220902/http://www.yushunews.com/system/2010/07/21/010163652.shtml |archive-date=2014-10-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[第十三世达赖喇嘛|达赖喇嘛]]电至[[英属印度|英属印度]]政府求援。英国对[[南京|南京]]中央施压，要求国府宣布停火<ref>{{cite book | last=Richardson|first=Hugh E. |author-link=黎吉生|year=1984|title=''Tibet and its History''| url=https://archive.org/details/tibetitshistory0000rich|edition=2nd Edition|pages=[https://archive.org/details/tibetitshistory0000rich/page/134 134]–136 | publisher=Shambhala Publications|location=Boston|isbn=0-87773-376-7}}</ref>。马刘与达赖双方互派代表签订《岗拖停战协定》，康藏以金沙江为界；后1933年6月15日正式签订《青藏和约》停止战争，青海军退回青海<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&ct=result&id=YD0sAQAAIAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang|title=The Journal of the Oriental Society of Australia, Volumes 31-34|author=Oriental Society of Australia|year=2000|publisher=Oriental Society of Australia|location=|pages=35, 37|isbn=|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034322/http://books.google.com/books?ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&ct=result&id=YD0sAQAAIAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang|archive-date=2014-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite conference|url=http://books.google.com/books?ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&ct=result&id=P3tpAAAAMAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang+tibetans|title=''Historical themes and current change in Central and Inner Asia''|conference=The Central and Inner Asian Seminar, University of Toronto, April 25–26, 1997|volume=1997|author=Michael Gervers, Wayne Schlepp, Joint Centre for Asia Pacific Studies|year=1998|publisher=Joint Centre for Asia Pacific Studies|location=|pages=73,74,76,195|isbn=1-895296-34-X|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034319/http://books.google.com/books?ei=hBshTPqEIsGqlAf_9rDHBA&ct=result&id=P3tpAAAAMAAJ&dq=ma+bufang+liu+wenhui&q=ma+bufang+tibetans|archive-date=2014-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.historyguy.com/tibet_china_wars_conflicts.html |title=''Wars and Conflicts Between Tibet and China'' |access-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019160524/http://www.historyguy.com/tibet_china_wars_conflicts.html |archive-date=2014-10-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。青海与西康在获胜后联合庆祝<ref>[http://www.ubcpress.ca/books/pdf/chapters/2006/tibetandnationalistchina'sfrontier.pdf Tibet and Nationalist China’s Frontier] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110513045337/http://www.ubcpress.ca/books/pdf/chapters/2006/tibetandnationalistchina'sfrontier.pdf |date=2011-05-13 }}</ref>。

